:"憤你老母場咩<br />\n<br />\n個場有幾憤呀？憤唔憤得過at力場呀，憤唔奮得過av力場呀？奮唔奮得過atv力場呀？<br />\n<br />\n我是憤怒你是憤場呀粉腸"},{"pid":"f5c8121e157ff405d419bdc50bb930ada3d3fa54","tid":41701,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i72.photobucket.com/albums/i187/hidecatcat/HoManTin/HoManTin5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi72.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fi187%2Fhidecatcat%2FHoManTin%2FHoManTin5.jpg&h=b5f24998&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n地鐵站？"},{"pid":"a2319dda154951730791c48063def1fd2f729f2e","tid":41701,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>憤你老母場咩<br />\n<br />\n個場有幾憤呀？憤唔憤得過at力場呀，憤唔奮得過av力場呀？奮唔奮得過atv力場呀？<br />\n<br />\n我是憤怒你是憤場呀粉腸</blockquote><br />\n咁激動做乜"},{"pid":"acc7e51c259d834e9a18f981291f64b9270d9231","tid":41701,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:30:32.000Z","msg":"憤青墳場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998f8130d6e930bb00f741c4240fb6a425b4a5eb","tid":41701,"uid":64701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:39:25.000Z","msg":"「憤場」是指憤怒之場所<br />\n<br />\n憤怒之場所與佛教中的修羅之場類似<br />\n<br />\n修羅之場一般解說紛爭，永無安寧的日子<br />\n<br />\n樓主問我們希望葬身那一種修羅戰場<br />\n<br />\n現今社會，戰爭減少，各個行業競爭激烈，毫無疑問是另一種的戰場<br />\n<br />\n香港普遍戰場有會計、保險、金融等俗稱「閪工」的行業<br />\n<br />\n跟住我已經唔想寫落去"},{"pid":"4c6534bf0770e9bd221eacd3a11d356eed68fcc6","tid":41701,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:41:39.000Z","msg":"我要污染大海<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce136f1faf92914eae21182ecc00699ac4097869","tid":41701,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:05:46.000Z","msg":"現時本港共有三個指定地點，包括塔門以東、東龍洲以東及西博寮海峽以南海域供海上撒灰。<br />\n<br />\n我揀東龍洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41152e